    "\n",
    "## 🚨 Common Pitfalls to Avoid\n",
    "\n",
    "### 1. Data Leakage\n",
    "❌ **Wrong:** Scale data before train-test split  \n",
    "✅ **Right:** Split first, then scale each separately\n",
    "\n",
    "### 2. Overfitting\n",
    "❌ **Wrong:** Tree depth = None (unlimited)  \n",
    "✅ **Right:** Limit max_depth, use cross-validation\n",
    "\n",
    "### 3. Not Understanding the Algorithm\n",
    "❌ **Wrong:** Copy code without understanding  \n",
    "✅ **Right:** Watch videos, draw tree on paper, trace through manually\n",
    "\n",
    "### 4. Skipping Preprocessing\n",
    "❌ **Wrong:** Jump straight to modeling  \n",
